quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  67,13,"Waasirroo qawlakum awi ijharoo bihi innahuAAaleemun bithati assudoor"
  67,14,"Ala yaAAlamu man khalaqa wahuwa allateefualkhabeer"
  67,15,"Huwa allathee jaAAala lakumu al-ardathaloolan famshoo fee manakibihawakuloo min rizqihi wa-ilayhi annushoor"
  67,16,"Aamintum man fee assama-i anyakhsifa bikumu al-arda fa-itha hiya tamoor"
  67,17,"Am amintum man fee assama-ian yursila AAalaykum hasiban fasataAAlamoona kayfa natheer"
  67,18,"Walaqad kaththaba allatheenamin qablihim fakayfa kana nakeer"
  67,19,"Awa lam yaraw ila attayrifawqahum saffatin wayaqbidna mayumsikuhunna illa arrahmanu innahubikulli shay-in baseer"
  67,20,"Amman hatha allathee huwajundun lakum yansurukum min dooni arrahmaniini alkafiroona illa fee ghuroor"
  67,21,"Amman hatha allatheeyarzuqukum in amsaka rizqahu bal lajjoo fee AAutuwwin wanufoor"
  67,22,"Afaman yamshee mukibban AAala wajhihiahda amman yamshee sawiyyan AAala siratinmustaqeem"
  67,23,"Qul huwa allathee anshaakum wajaAAalalakumu assamAAa wal-absara wal-af-idataqaleelan ma tashkuroon"
  67,24,"Qul huwa allathee tharaakumfee al-ardi wa-ilayhi tuhsharoon"
  67,25,"Wayaqooloona mata hathaalwaAAdu in kuntum sadiqeen"
  67,26,"Qul innama alAAilmu AAinda Allahiwa-innama ana natheerun mubeen"
